1. *Ubijem* ga ako ponovo pokusava da me prevari. (I will kill him if he tries to cheat on me again.)
2. Ne mogu da *ubijem* nikoga. (I can't kill anyone.)
3. *Ubila* je svoju najbolju prijateljicu. (She killed her best friend.)
4. Ja bih te *ubio* da mogu. (I would kill you if I could.)
5. Oni su *ubili* sve ljude u gradu. (They killed all the people in the town.)
6. *Ubij* moju bol! (Kill my pain!)